<F P=100> Colombia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Search `Unsuccessful So Far' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Search `Unsuccessful So Far' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA0104223394 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network in 
Spanish 2208 GMT 1 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA0104223394 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Santa Fe de Bogota -- The search for Ramon Rissin, 
Summer Linguistic Institute security chief, has been 
unsuccessful so far. Alleged FARC [Revolutionary Armed Forces 
of Colombia] guerrillas allegedly kidnapped him on the road 
between Puerto Lleras and Loma Linda, where the institute's main 
office is located. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

