<H3> <TI>   Chamber Shelves Prosecution of Resigned Deputies </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Chamber Shelves Prosecution of Resigned Deputies </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY2903032494 Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL in Portuguese 
25 Mar 94 p 1--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PY2903032494 </F>
<F P=104>  Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL </F>
<F P=105>  Portuguese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] By a vote of 23 to 8, the Constitution and Justice 
Committee of the Chamber of Deputies has decided to shelve the 
prosecution proceedings on former Deputies Joao Alves, Genebaldo 
Correia, Cid Carvalho, and Manoel Moreira, who were charged with 
having been members of the budget gang. They resigned their 
posts early in the week to prevent being dismissed. With the 
exception of Joao Alves, who has no party, they can run for a 
seat in the Chamber in the next elections. 

</TEXT>

