  [Text] A U.S. State Department report acknowledges Cuba's 
cooperation in the war against international drug trafficking. 
This report confirms that Cuban authorities support antidrug 
policies. Cuban efforts in this regard include the interception 
of planes and ships, as well as supplying information to U.S. 
agencies involved in this struggle. 

</TEXT>

