<H3> <TI>   Official Urges Measures To End Deforestation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Official Urges Measures To End Deforestation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL0504180094 Havana Radio Progreso Network in Spanish 1100 
GMT 5 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL0504180094 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Progreso Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At the council of the Ministry of Agriculture's 
national directorate, Vice Minister of Agriculture (Aguedo 
Morales) sharply criticized the indiscriminate chopping down of 
trees and theft and misappropriation of the wood, which are 
crimes against the nation's patrimony that affect the economy. 
(Morales) called for strong measures to avoid a repetition of 
such acts. 

</TEXT>

