<F P=106> [From the "Swann" column by Ricardo Boechat] </F>
  [Text] The following is the outcome of a meeting held 
yesterday in Beijing by Brazilian Foreign Minister Celso Amorim 
and PRC Foreign Minister Qian Qichen: 
  Brazil will support the PRC's entry into GATT. 
  In return, the PRC will vote in favor of the expansion of 
