<H3> <TI>   Pastrana Demands Investigation of Wiretapping </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Pastrana Demands Investigation of Wiretapping </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA0604041194 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 in Spanish 0000 GMT 5 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA0604041194 </F>
<F P=104>  Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 
1 </F>

<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "24 Hours Newscast"] </F>
  [Text] Andres Pastrana Arango, New Democratic Force's 
presidential candidate, demanded a thorough investigation of the 
delicate wiretapping incident reported by the SEMANA magazine. 
  [Begin recording] [Pastrana] The incident is very serious. 
The country expects it to be clarified. We cannot understand 
how a group as important as the Santo Domingo Group can be 
involved in wiretapping, as the magazine reported. Today, the 
country demands an explanation. It is important to clarify this 
problem. 
  [Reporter] Will the government intervene? 
  [Pastrana] It should. Reports have been filed with the 
attorney general. [end recording] 

