<H3> <TI>   Meets Uruguayan President, Bank Director </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Meets Uruguayan President, Bank Director </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PA0604122694 Havana PRENSA LATINA in Spanish 0156 GMT 5 Apr 
94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

