<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Editorial Report] Havana PRENSA LATINA in Spanish at 1509 
GMT on 1 April 1994 reports that Mexican Cubamor Travel Agency 
has announced it will send approximately 6,000 tourists to Cuba 
this year. According to Company Manager Bernardo Uriostegue 
Najera, this figure represents a hearty 10 percent of the total 
number of Mexican vacationers traveling to Cuba. The agency 
expects to begin moving cargo to and from Cuba soon. 

