<H3> <TI>   Prosecutors To Join Antinarcotics Operation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Prosecutors To Join Antinarcotics Operation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY0704000894 Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network in 
Spanish 1800 GMT 6 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY0704000894 </F>
<F P=104>  Lima Radio Programas del Peru Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Attorney General's Office authorized special 
provincial prosecutors for drug cases in Pucallpa, to 
participate in the joint antinarcotics operations carried out 
throughout the country. 
  For this purpose, the prosecutors must coordinate their 
participation with the Armed Forces joint command, the Peruvian 
National Police Antinarcotics Division, the DEA, and the U.S. 
Embassy antinarcotics department. 
  If special prosecutors Juan Malca Perez, Roberto Pesantes 
Creder, Luis Valdivia Susunaga, and Jorge Requifo Rojas find 
evidence of crimes, they must inform the provincial prosecutor 
of the respective jurisdiction so he can adopt the measures 
established by law. 

</TEXT>

